N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 670.16 - Transferred CPLR article 78 proceedings

State Regulations
CPLR article 78 proceedings
transferred to this court pursuant to CPLR 7804(g) may be prosecuted in
accordance with any of the methods specified in section
670.9
of this Part. Where
applicable, every such proceeding shall be governed by this Part as if it were
an appeal. Notes
